de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.core

Class LexicalResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.core.LexicalResource

  • public class LexicalResource
extends Object
    LexicalResource is a class representing the entire resource. The Lexical Resource instance is a container for at least one or more lexicons.
    Author:
    Zijad Maksuti
    See Also:
    Lexicon
